{"article_id":"VTLdy38Q4Q5JXgT2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Trump administration will push ahead with efforts","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to add a citizenship question to the 2020 census ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"despite announcing the plan had been dropped .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"President Trump sowed confusion on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"he was `` moving forward '' with the controversial plan .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"This came a day after his own senior officials said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"the census papers would be printed without the question .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"It leaves the future of the census ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"which determines electoral districts and federal funding ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"in some doubt .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"The administration has argued","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"that a citizenship question would bolster protections for minority voters ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"but opponents fear","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"it would deter immigrant households from taking part .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Democrats and civil rights groups believe","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"the question could ultimately lead to millions of people","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"- mostly Latinos and African Americans -","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"not being counted .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Last week , the Supreme Court temporarily blocked the citizenship question","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"and said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"the government 's justification","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"for including it","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"seemed `` contrived '' .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Then , on Tuesday , the government appeared to back down altogether","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"when Commerce Secretary Wilbur Ross announced","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that the census questionnaires were being printed","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"without it .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"But in a series of later tweets , President Trump said","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he would do `` whatever is necessary ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to ensure","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"the question was included .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"His latest tweet blindsided senior officials","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"who have since been working frantically","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to find a legal means","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"to include the question ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"US media report .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"`` We at the Department of Justice have been instructed to examine whether there is a path forward","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"consistent with the Supreme Court decision","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that would allow us to include the citizenship question on the census , ''","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Assistant Attorney General Joseph Hunt told a Maryland-based federal judge on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` We think","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"there may be a legally available path .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"We 're examining that ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"looking at near-term options","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"to see","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"whether that 's viable and possible , ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Tight print deadlines and a complex legal picture mean the administration is likely to face a difficult battle .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"The papers will reportedly be printed","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"without the question","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"while officials examine their options .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"This question has not appeared on a US census for all Americans since 1950 ,","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"though it has been asked to some subsets of the population between 1970 and 2000 .","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"The population count helps the government draw up districts for state and local elections ,","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"and determine how much federal funding each state receives","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"- a matter of hundreds of billions of dollars .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"In a 2018 report , Census Bureau researchers found","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that the inclusion of a citizenship question could suppress response rates in households with immigrants and minority groups ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"leading to a `` lower-quality population count '' .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"But Mr Ross","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"- the billionaire financier","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"who oversees the Census Bureau -","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"insisted","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that detailed citizenship data would be of `` greater importance than any adverse effect ''","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"posed by an undercount .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"The White House argues","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that the decision","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"to include the question","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"was made for practical reasons .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"`` When you have a census","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and you 're not allowed to talk about whether or not somebody 's a citizen or not ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that does n't sound so good to me , ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Mr Trump said to reporters last month .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"But critics argue","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"it is politically motivated","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and it would suppress responses from immigrants and racial minorities .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"They believe","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"this would benefit the Republican Party","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"when it came to the drawing-up of districts for elections","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"and calculating how much funding each state receives .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"The states with the highest immigration populations , such as California and New Mexico , would be at the greatest risk of an undercount .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Many of these states tend to vote Democrat .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Depressed response rates in these states would allow for electorate boundaries to be redrawn ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"pulling political power","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"- and funding -","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"away from Democratic-leaning , minority households .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Last week , the Supreme Court wrote in a 5-4 ruling","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that the Trump administration had not provided adequate justification for the inclusion of the question .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Three federal judges had earlier issued rulings","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"to block the question ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"one","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"calling it a threat `` to the very foundation '' of US democracy .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":111,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":103,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":95,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":94,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":3,"right":96,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":106,"right":109,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"adversative","nuclear